PHP-MRC

> cd /usr/src/php-4.3.8/ext 
> cvs co -d mrc php_mrc


*1.  -- build PHP with MRC support --

	> cd /usr/src/php-4.3.8/
	> ./buildconf --force
	> ./configure --prefix=/usr/share --datadir=/usr/share/php --bindir=/usr/bin --libdir=/usr/share --includedir=/usr/include --with-_lib=lib --with-config-file-path=/etc --with-exec-dir=/usr/lib/php/bin --with-jpeg-dir=/usr --with-zlib=yes --with-gd --enable-mrc --with-apxs=/usr/sbin/apxs

	> make
	> make install


*2. -- build MRC as a php shared extension

	> cd /usr/src/php-4.3.8/ext/mrc/
	> phpize
	> ./configure
	> make
	> make install
